room_title: Escape room "Case Closed Montclair" by Amazing Escape Room in New York
review: This was not amazing at all, quite underwhelming to be frank. Definitely not worth the $30, go see a movie instead.

room_title: Escape room "Case Closed Montclair" by Amazing Escape Room in New York
